  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4 60 \u0d89\u0d9a\u0dca\u0db8\u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0dbb\u0da2\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dd0. 31\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db8 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dec. to government employees who are over 60 years old. Will have to retire before 31st",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In his budget speech, the President said that the mandatory retirement age of employees of government and semi-government institutions will be reduced to 60 years and all government employees who are currently over 60 years old should retire by December 31."
      ],
